1. Decide which pizze place to eat from
2. Choose what type of pizza you want
3. Decide if you want sides with pizza
4. Call and order pizza
5. Wait for pizza
6. Pay for pizza once delivered
7. Eat pizza 
8. If sent wrong order, tell the delivery driver
9. Call the pizza place 
10. Tell them that you received the wring order
11. Ask them to send the correct order
12. Confirm that it is the correct order
13. Wait for new pizza